@node Main "Pyramid - Documentation"

                             'Pyramid' V1.2

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Pyramid' is a @{"game" link play} where the goal is to find the Pharaoh's tomb
which is located at the top of the pyramid. To get to the tomb, you
must move in a maze of corridors and ladders that you have to climb
up or down.

  To complicate matters, only a small portion (a 5 by 5 tile area)
of the pyramid is shown.

  Have fun!

             @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
             @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
             @{"         History           " link histo}
